        <p style="font-size:14.5px;line-height:1.7;color:#555;margin:0;">Cracked, cloudy, or leaking glass block gets pulled and replaced with new block or a hopper conversion, your choice.</p>
      </div>
      <div style="background:#fff;border:1px solid #e3ded4;border-radius:10px;padding:26px;box-shadow:0 2px 8px rgba(14,77,110,0.05);">
        <h3 style="font-family:'Nunito Sans',sans-serif;font-size:18px;font-weight:800;color:#0A3D5C;margin:0 0 8px;">Frame Rot and Rust Repair</h3>
        <p style="font-size:14.5px;line-height:1.7;color:#555;margin:0;">We rebuild soft wood framing and cut out rusted steel before the new window goes in, so it's not sitting on a bad base.</p>
      </div>
      <div style="background:#fff;border:1px solid #e3ded4;border-radius:10px;padding:26px;box-shadow:0 2px 8px rgba(14,77,110,0.05);">
        <h3 style="font-family:'Nunito Sans',sans-serif;font-size:18px;font-weight:800;color:#0A3D5C;margin:0 0 8px;">Moisture and Seal Correction</h3>
        <p style="font-size:14.5px;line-height:1.7;color:#555;margin:0;">We reset flashing and re-caulk the perimeter so water stops tracking into the frame and the wall cavity behind it.</p>
      </div>
      <div style="background:#fff;border:1px solid #e3ded4;border-radius:10px;padding:26px;box-shadow:0 2px 8px rgba(14,77,110,0.05);">
        <h3 style="font-family:'Nunito Sans',sans-serif;font-size:18px;font-weight:800;color:#0A3D5C;margin:0 0 8px;">Energy Efficiency Upgrades</h3>
